Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…  怎么说才好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.29,0:20:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…  半结局…
